[I] An online gaming center with multiple rooms and game modules

[T] The GGZ Gaming Zone (GGZ) is an Internet gaming center. Players login
[T] and sit at tables where they can play their favorite games and chat with
[T] other players. GGZ can support multiple rooms with varying skill levels.

[U] http://www.ggzgamingzone.org/

